sequenceDiagram
    Note over User,Webapp: User must be logged in
    User ->>+ Webapp: click GROUPS navbar button
    Webapp ->> Gateway Service: axios.get('/user/group/list')
    Gateway Service ->> Users: axios.get('/user/group/list')

    Users ->> MariaDB: router.get('/user/group/list')
    MariaDB -->> Users: JSON response

    Users -->> Gateway Service: 
    Gateway Service -->> Webapp: 
    Webapp -->>- User: show groups list and group creation form

    loop Create a group
        User ->>+ Webapp: insert a group name and click CREATE button
        Webapp ->> Gateway Service: axios.post('/group/add')
        Gateway Service ->> Users: axios.post('/group/add')

        Users ->> MariaDB: router.post('/user/group/add')
        MariaDB -->> Users: JSON response

        Users -->> Gateway Service: 
        Gateway Service -->> Webapp: 
        Webapp -->>- User: update the groups view
    end